'''Docking Bay 87''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|docking bay]] in the city of [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. It was situated across from [[Docking Bay 86]]. It was the same size as most bays, but had been modernized and thus became one of the favorite docking bays in Mos Eisley. The standard fee was thirty [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] a day.

During [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]], the bay was owned by an [[Ishi Tib/Legends|Ishi Tib]] named [[Dr'xureretue]], who was commonly known as Drue.<ref name="GG7" />

